data.title: MR - Hilario Sayson Malagueño Mr. Noel Cesar Lumabad Mrs - Leonor Ibarreta Malagueño Mrs. Violeta Almonte Lumabad
data.meta_description: WEDDING (1) - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document is an invitation to a wedding ceremony between Marynor and Jerome that will take place on October 24th, 2029 at 9:00 AM at St. Michael the Archangel Parish Church in Oas, Albay, Philippines. It provides the names of the officiating priests, bridal party members, sponsors, and reception details following the ceremony.
